It is necessary to inform the Greek people, in the most formal way of where we are & for where we want to go #vouli
Our proposal as a whole is the only realistic basis for discussing a #vouli agreement
The entire government's reform effort to succeed requires a meaningful solution to the debt problem. #vouli
We do not just need an agreement. We need a solution. A final solution, both for Greece and for Europe. #vouli
A solution that will end the policy of unrealistic surpluses & austerity & will ensure debt sustainability. #vouli
The suggestion given to me by President Yugger, on behalf of the three institutions, surprised me unpleasantly. #vouli
It is obvious that the Greek Government can not in any case consent to unreasonable proposals. #vouli
Today I would like to hear the opposition if it calls on us to accept the proposal tabled by the three institutions. #vouli
The world is asking only one thing: Let us not depart from our righteous demands. Do not bow to unreasonable demands. #vouli
The realistic approach of the Greek side is the only serious bargaining line. #vouli
The Greek issue is not isolated but concerns the whole of the Eurozone and its outlook. # Vouli
To summarize the strategic goal of the Greek government in the ongoing negotiations #vouli
Low primary surpluses Debt restructuring Pension & real wage protection #vouli
Redistribution of income for the benefit of the majority Resumption of collective bargaining Reversal of deregulation of work. #vouli
A strong investment program that will create a positive shock for the Greek economy, mobilizing its pocketing potential. #vouli
Now is the time of responsibility for everyone. And for the opposition. I urge you to honestly support the national effort. #vouli
We will best defend the right of a whole people to live with dignity and prosperity in prosperity. #vouli
